00:42:16,450 --> 00:42:19,036
that I think many of us
really were not aware of.

786
00:42:19,119 --> 00:42:19,995
Yeah.

787
00:42:20,079 --> 00:42:24,333
Because I was going around the country
doing big, huge rallies.

788
00:42:24,416 --> 00:42:25,543
It was so much fun.

