Over the course of the campaign,

808
00:43:20,764 --> 00:43:22,641
I was telling my story.

809
00:43:22,725 --> 00:43:24,393
I was being vulnerable.

810
00:43:24,685 --> 00:43:26,061
Let me tell you something.

811
00:43:26,145 --> 00:43:29,523
For the first time in my adult lifetime,

812
00:43:29,607 --> 00:43:31,525
I'm really proud of my country.

813
00:43:31,609 --> 00:43:35,738
And not just because Barack has done well,

814
00:43:35,821 --> 00:43:39,033
but because I think
people are hungry for change.

815
00:43:40,034 --> 00:43:42,494
And to have that distorted,

816
00:43:42,703 --> 00:43:44,830
it just felt so wrong.

817
00:43:45,497 --> 00:43:48,208
Does Michelle Obama dislike America?

818
00:43:48,292 --> 00:43:50,502
I think she's got a chip on her shoulder.

819
00:43:50,586 --> 00:43:52,254
She has a Stokely Carmichael

