01:14:11,447 --> 01:14:12,698
It's nice to see you.

1265
01:14:13,365 --> 01:14:15,242
What were you all going to talk about?

1266
01:14:15,325 --> 01:14:17,953
Becoming.

1267
01:14:18,036 --> 01:14:19,288
I want to eavesdrop.

1268
01:14:19,371 --> 01:14:21,707
We saw you last night,

1269
01:14:22,040 --> 01:14:27,379
and you said that
