1270
01:14:27,754 --> 01:14:31,008
So I want to ask our group,

1271
01:14:31,091 --> 01:14:34,261
what advice would you give our First Lady?

1272
01:14:34,553 --> 01:14:38,307
The first reaction, really,
is you've got to find your life again.

1273
01:14:38,390 --> 01:14:40,434
There are so many different phases of you,

1274
01:14:40,517 --> 01:14:43,145
and a lot of them you forget
while you're childrearing,

1275
01:14:43,228 --> 01:14:44,813
and married, and all that stuff.

1276
01:14:44,897 --> 01:14:47,858
So my advice to you
is just do what you're doing.

1277
01:14:48,066 --> 01:14:50,360
- Keep on doing it.
- Yes.

1278
01:14:50,444 --> 01:14:53,739
As my mother says, give it some time.

1279
01:14:54,156 --> 01:14:56,658
And I'm so glad you did not get yourself

1280
01:14:57,367 --> 01:15:02,247
wrapped up in the fluff
of being the First Lady

1281
01:15:02,331 --> 01:15:04,124
and living in the White House,

1282
01:15:04,208 --> 01:15:06,460
and, "My husband is..."

1283
01:15:09,338 --> 01:15:12,174
Your view of me matters.

1284
01:15:12,466 --> 01:15:16,261
Every time we showed up,
we showed up to make you all proud.

1285
01:15:16,345 --> 01:15:18,680
Right. And you did. You did that.

1286
01:15:19,515 --> 01:15:23,936
When I saw you on television,
when you were inaugurated,

1287
01:15:24,228 --> 01:15:27,940
I said, "I never thought
that I would ever see..."

1288
01:15:28,023 --> 01:15:29,858
Right.
My mother said the same thing.

1289
01:15:29,942 --> 01:15:35,489
And I look back, and my mother
and my father had never seen it.

1290
01:15:36,281 --> 01:15:38,033
But it was something.

1291
01:15:38,116 --> 01:15:41,370
- I thank you and Barack for that.
- You saw it for them.

1292
01:15:41,453 --> 01:15:42,579
I saw it.

1293
01:15:42,871 --> 01:15:44,498
So it is a blessing.

1294
01:15:44,581 --> 01:15:47,334
- Yeah.
- Michelle, I thank you.

1295
01:15:47,668 --> 01:15:49,002
So God is good.

1296
01:15:49,086 --> 01:15:52,589
- And you will always be First Lady to me.
- You will always be First Lady.

1297
01:15:52,673 --> 01:15:55,384
- Forever First Lady.
- You will always be First Lady.

