Oh, it's a selfie-cam!

1315
01:16:54,943 --> 01:16:56,945
- Yes.
- That will come in handy.

1316
01:16:57,029 --> 01:16:58,780
Look at the camera, not the remote.

1317
01:16:59,197 --> 01:17:00,198
OK.

1318
01:17:04,995 --> 01:17:06,955
What's next in life?

1319
01:17:11,293 --> 01:17:13,795
I want to keep working
with young people.

1320
01:17:15,547 --> 01:17:19,051
The future of our nation
is up to the next generation.

1321
01:17:19,635 --> 01:17:21,595
But I know that doesn't just happen.

1322
01:17:22,012 --> 01:17:24,056
Young people need some encouragement.

1323
01:17:24,306 --> 01:17:25,849
You've got my eyelashes.

1324
01:17:26,767 --> 01:17:27,851
Hi, Michelle.

1325
01:17:28,143 --> 01:17:30,395
All right, get it done. Get it done.

1326
01:17:31,063 --> 01:17:32,272
How are you?

1327
01:17:34,691 --> 01:17:38,403
I love you. You guys
are up next, OK? So proud of you.

1328
01:17:40,072 --> 01:17:41,865
Barack and I are empty-nesters,

1329
01:17:41,948 --> 01:17:44,326
and that has been exhilarating:

1330
01:17:44,409 --> 01:17:48,413
to watch the two little beings
you were in charge of grow up.

1331
01:17:50,624 --> 01:17:54,294
I'm excited for her
to be proud of what she's done,

1332
01:17:54,378 --> 01:17:57,381
because I think that's the most important
thing for a human to do:

1333
01:17:57,464 --> 01:17:58,674
to be proud of themselves.

1334
01:17:59,216 --> 01:18:02,219
No longer facing that same scrutiny,

1335
01:18:02,302 --> 01:18:05,764
being able to let all of that
leave your mind,

1336
01:18:06,348 --> 01:18:07,641
creates so much more space.

1337
01:18:16,817 --> 01:18:18,777
I want to take care of me,

1338
01:18:19,861 --> 01:18:21,238
rediscover my husband...

1339
01:18:23,865 --> 01:18:26,785
My life is starting to be mine again.

1340
01:18:29,454 --> 01:18:33,125
There is another chapter
waiting for me out there.

