1407
01:23:15,615 --> 01:23:20,996
...who realizes that I have the power
to change the world.

1408
01:23:21,413 --> 01:23:22,330
Yeah!

1409
01:23:32,048 --> 01:23:34,551
I am a nonbinary human.

1410
01:23:37,637 --> 01:23:39,973
And I am becoming brave

1411
01:23:40,056 --> 01:23:42,183
and unafraid to live openly,

1412
01:23:42,267 --> 01:23:44,561
truthfully and joyfully.

1413
01:23:54,904 --> 01:23:57,991
I am becoming a mom
who is teaching my teenage boys

1414
01:23:58,074 --> 01:24:02,120
to value and respect strong,
smart, independent women.

1415
01:24:02,203 --> 01:24:03,538
Woohoo!

1416
01:24:04,372 --> 01:24:05,373
Thank you!

1417
01:24:13,465 --> 01:24:15,759
My parents emigrated from Mexico,

